Package: CleanFHU
Title: Data Cleaning and Pipeline Tools for Pregnancy and Mortality Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Dr.Fredrick Omondi Onduru
Maintainer: The package maintainer <fredrickonduru@gmail.com>
Description: CleanFHU provides a standardised, reproducible workflow for cleaning,
    classifying, and harmonising pregnancy and maternal/neonatal mortality study data.
    It wraps common data preparation steps — demographic recoding, clinical variable
    classification, biomarker thresholds, water/sanitation/energy (WASH) coding, and
    anemia grading — into composable, well-documented functions so that multi-site
    PRISMA-aligned studies can share a single pipeline with minimal friction.
